{"tid":1171391,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"離鄉別井拍《倚天》　許雅婷點睇小昭？","createTime":"2019-05-25T16:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T13:41:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"925af48bbd1adaa8b974058da4b6b22a7158996d","tid":1171391,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/photo/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190526000335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190526000335&h=cf24fb2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/photo/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190526000335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190526000335&h=973a5202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個女仔北上拍劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/photo/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190526000335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190526000335&h=161f3725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係唔簡單㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/photo/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190526000335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190526%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190526000335&h=27070052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家又鍾唔鍾意呢個小昭呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訪問:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190526%2Fbkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001.html&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=90f9b057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190526/bkn-20190526000041772-0526_00862_001.html</a><br />\n新版《倚天屠龍記》依家喺無綫熱播，當中波斯聖女小昭就由香港藝人許雅婷所飾演。<br />\n<br />\n小說中以「雙目湛湛有神，修眉端鼻，頰邊微現梨渦，直是秀美無倫...雖然容貌絕麗，卻掩不住容顏中的稚氣...」嚟描述小昭。許雅婷五觀標緻，有啲異國風情，貼合番小昭擁有4份之1嘅波斯血統，24歲嘅許雅婷臉上仲有小小稚氣，完美Carry呢個角色！<br />\n<br />\n今次東網搵嚟許雅婷做專訪，想知佢點睇小昭呢個角色？佢返內地拍劇感覺又係點？邊一個場口佢又係鍾意？未來有咩工作大計？咁就快啲去片，睇睇許雅婷嘅內心世界喇！ <br />\n<br />\n好想佢騎上黎 係咁叫我公子....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03b8aa5635281d0d19d2f5e037a494dd44a7ef4","tid":1171391,"uid":74065,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLv1O92.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLv1O92.gif&h=9ca1ca29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2f508dcf24c7cb82747e752a06568746e942a57","tid":1171391,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b03b8aa5635281d0d19d2f5e037a494dd44a7ef4","tid":1171391,"uid":74065,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLv1O92.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLv1O92.gif&h=9ca1ca29&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"咩戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb025b8a8fc1605dd029e25adbdf851f14e0849","tid":1171391,"uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e2f508dcf24c7cb82747e752a06568746e942a57","tid":1171391,"uid":110570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b03b8aa5635281d0d19d2f5e037a494dd44a7ef4","tid":1171391,"uid":74065,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2